I've got a good market for sow potions, the only problem I've started to run into is people undercutting the market for sow potions.  Granted, sow potions aren't the most expensive ones, but by far the one that you will make the most money on for the effort and the one most people will buy.  Just a few thoughts, if people would stick with a market value, everyone would make money and the people who need the potions would buy rather then *****ing about how someone else is selling for 80pp and that's all they are worth.<BR> <BR>/rant off
